ZH: 今天是三月份。
EN: Today is March.

ZH: 我家有三口人。
EN: There are three people in my family.

ZH: 我有三只猫。
EN: I have three cats.

ZH: 他们是三个好朋友。
EN: They are three good friends.

ZH: 这本书有三百页。
EN: This book has three hundred pages.

ZH: 他们三个一起去了海滩。
EN: The three of them went to the beach together.

ZH: 学校里有三个操场。
EN: There are three playgrounds in the school.

ZH: 我有三个兄弟姐妹。
EN: I have three siblings.

ZH: 他三岁的时候学会了说话。
EN: He learned to speak when he was three years old.

ZH: 三个小时后我们会到达目的地。
EN: We will reach our destination in three hours.

ZH: 我们学了三个小时的数学课。
EN: We studied math for three hours.

ZH: 星期三是我最喜欢的一天。
EN: Wednesday is my favorite day of the week.

ZH: 请把那三个苹果给我。
EN: Please give me those three apples.

ZH: 你能找到三个词组含有“三”吗？
EN: Can you find three phrases that contain the word "三"?

ZH: 他们每三个月去一次图书馆。
EN: They go to the library every three months.

ZH: 这本杂志需要三天才能读完。
EN: It takes three days to finish reading this magazine.

ZH: 我三点半下班。
EN: I get off work at three thirty.

ZH: 请给我三杯咖啡。
EN: Please give me three cups of coffee.

ZH: 三个人站在那里。
EN: Three people are standing there.

ZH: 明天是三号。
EN: Tomorrow is the third.
